hadiths[6]{hadithnumber,text}:
2008,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke fazaail bayan farma rahe they ke jo shakhs bhi usmein eman aur niyat ajr w sawab ke sath (raat mein) Namaz ke liye khada ho iske pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jaengey."
2009,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne Ramazan ki raaton main ( bedaar reh kar) namaaze-Taraaveeh padhi, eman aur sawab ki niyat ke saath, iske agley tamam gunah maaf ho jaengey. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur logon ka yahi haal raha (alag-alag akeley aur jamaton se Taraaveeh padhtey they) iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat main aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke shuruati daure-khilaafat mein bhi aisa hi raha."
2010,"main umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Ramazan ki aik raat ko masjid mein gaya. sab log alag-alag aur muntashir they, koi akelaa Namaz padh raha tha, aur kuchh kisi ke peechhey khadey huey they. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, mera khayal hai ke agar main tamam logon ko aik qaari ke peechhey jama kar dun to zyada achchha hoga, chunanche aap ne yahi thaan kar Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka imam bana diya. phir aik raat jo main unke sath nikla to dekha ke log apne imam ke peechhey Namaz ( Taraaveeh ( padh rahe hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, ye nayaa tariqa behtar aur munasib hai aur) raat ka ( wo hissey jis mein ye log so jatey hain us hissey se behtar aur afzal hai jis mein ye Namaz padhtey hain. aap ki murad raat ke aakhiri hisse (ki fazeelat) se thi kyonke log ye Namaz raat ke shuru hi mein padh letey they."
2011,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik baar Namaz ( Taraaveeh ( padhi aur ye Ramazan mein hua tha.
2012,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik martaba ( Ramazan ki) nisf shab mein masjid tashrif le gaey aur wahan Taraaveeh ki Namaz padhi. kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath Namaz mein Sharik ho gaey. subah hui to unhon-ne iska charcha kya. chunanche dusri raat mein log pahley se bhi zyada jama ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. dusri subah ko aur zyada charcha hua aur teesri raat us se bhi zyada log jama ho gaey. aap ne (is raat bhi) Namaz padhi aur logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) ki. chothi raat ko ye aalim tha ke masjid mein Namaz padhney aaney walon ke liye jagah bhi baqi nahi rahi thi. (lekin us raat aap bahar hi nahi aaye) balke subah ki Namaz ke liye bahar tashrif laey. jab Namaz padh li to logon ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar shahadat ke baad farmaya, ammaa ba'd! tumharey yahan jama honey ka mujhey ilm tha, lekin mujhey khof iska hua ke kahin ye Namaz tum par farz na kar di jaey aur phir tum uski adaaeygi se aajiz ho jao, chunanche jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to yahi kaifiyat qaaim rahi."
2013,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Taraaveeh ya tahajjud ki Namaz ( Ramazan mein kitni rakatein padhtey they? to unhon-ne batlaya ke Ramazan ho ya koi aur mahina aap gyara (11) rakaton se zyada nahi padhtey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pehli char rakaat padhtey, tum unke Husn w khoobi aur lambaai ka haal na poochho, phir char rakaat padhtey, unke bhi Husn w khoobi aur lambai ka haal na poochho, aakhir mein teen rakaat ( witr ( padhtey they. maine aik baar poochha, ya Rasulullah! kya aap witr padhney se pahley so jatey hain? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Aaisha ! meri aankhen soti hain lekin mera dil nahi sota."
